Name: test_early_abort
Description:
There have been some problems with conda-build dropping out early.
    Make sure we aren't causing them

Name: test_purge
Description:
purge clears out build folders - things like some_pkg_12048309850135

    It does not clear out build packages from folders like osx-64 or linux-64.

Name: test_purge_all
Description: purge-all clears out build folders as well as build packages in the osx-64 folders and such

This recipe requires the conda_build_test_requirement package, which is
    only on the conda_build_test channel. This verifies that the -c argument
    works.
